    "en": {
      "title": "Kandakhadu conflict: Inquiry report today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Commissioner General of Rehabilitation, Major General Darshana Hettiarachi, has said that he will receive the investigation report regarding the clash that took place last Tuesday night at Kantagadu Rehabilitation Centre.",
        "After receiving it, it will be handed over to Justice Minister Vijayadasa Rajapaksa, he said.",
        "A four-member committee was appointed to investigate the incident and submit a report.",
        "Of the approximately 800 prisoners who escaped during the unrest, 701 were arrested and remanded in custody.",
        "The Commissioner General of Rehabilitation mentioned that steps have been taken to find 27 more people."
      ],
